  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall aim with this project is to describe the correlation between measured and charted
      saturation after intensive care and also describe the saturation-pattern in these patients.
      The investigators will also correlate post-ICU desaturations measured as oxygen denaturation
      index and complications to pre-ICU obstructive sleep apnea and the STOP BANG screening
      questionnaire.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
